Introduction

DSSHOP所有API接口文档

本文档旨在提供您使用我们的API所需的所有信息。

当你滚动屏幕时，你会在右边的黑暗区域看到使用不同编程语言的API的代码示例(或作为移动内容的一部分)。 你可以通过右上角的选项卡切换语言(或者在移动设备上从左上角的导航菜单)。

Base URL

http://dsshop.test

Authenticating requests

This API is not authenticated.

config

配置 Class ConfigController

ConfigList 配置列表

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request GET \
    --get "http://dsshop.test/api/v1/admin/config?name=quas&limit=6&sort=explicabo&page=et" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(
    "http://dsshop.test/api/v1/admin/config"
);

const params = {
    "name": "quas",
    "limit": "6",
    "sort": "explicabo",
    "page": "et",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());

Example response (500):

access-control-expose-headers: Authorization, authenticated
access-control-allow-methods: GET, POST, PATCH, PUT, OPTIONS,DELETE
access-control-allow-credentials: true

curl --request POST \
    "http://dsshop.test/api/v1/admin/config/quae?id=19&name=modi&sort=8" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(
    "http://dsshop.test/api/v1/admin/config/quae"
);

    "id": "19",
    "name": "modi",
    "sort": "8",
};

    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

    method: "POST",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request POST \
    "http://dsshop.test/api/v1/admin/admin?name=repudiandae&email=voluptatibus&cellphone=15&portrait=sunt&password=illum" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(
    "http://dsshop.test/api/v1/admin/admin"
);

const params = {
    "name": "repudiandae",
    "email": "voluptatibus",
    "cellphone": "15",
    "portrait": "sunt",
    "password": "illum",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());

GET api/v1/admin/index

Upload 上传

requires authentication

Example request:
curl --request POST \
    "http://dsshop.test/api/v1/admin/uploadPictures?type=5&size=17&full=" \
    --header "Content-Type: multipart/form-data" \
    --header "Accept: application/json" \
    --form "file=@/tmp/phpTdBIcC" 
const url = new URL(
    "http://dsshop.test/api/v1/admin/uploadPictures"
);

const params = {
    "type": "5",
    "size": "17",
    "full": "0",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "multipart/form-data",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

const body = new FormData();
body.append('file', document.querySelector('input[name="file"]').files[0]);

fetch(url, {
    method: "POST",
    headers,
    body,
}).then(response => response.json());

);

SpecificationList 规格列表

Example request:
curl --request GET \
    --get "http://dsshop.test/api/v1/admin/specification?title=provident&limit=12&sort=et&page=fugiat" \
    --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
    --header "Accept: application/json"
const url = new URL(
    "http://dsshop.test/api/v1/admin/specification"
);

const params = {
    "title": "provident",
    "limit": "12",
    "sort": "et",
    "page": "fugiat",
};
Object.keys(params)
    .forEach(key => url.searchParams.append(key, params[key]));

const headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Accept": "application/json",
};

fetch(url, {
    method: "GET",
    headers,
}).then(response => response.json());
